1. *Nedostajao* mi je tvoj osmeh. (I missed your smile.)
2. Njemu je *nedostajala* hrabrost da kaže istinu. (He lacked the courage to tell the truth.)
3. Kada sam otišla, shvatila sam koliko mi je *nedostajalo* moje rodno mesto. (When I left, I realized how much I missed my hometown.)
4. *Nedostajali* su nam novi članovi u našem timu. (We were missing new members in our team.)
5. On je *nedostajao* na času engleskog jezika. (He was absent from the English class.)
6. Bez obzira koliko puta da je gledam, uvek mi *nedostaje* nešto u ovoj slici. (No matter how many times I look at it, there's always something missing in this picture for me.)
7. *Nedostajao* mi je osećaj slobode koji sam imala kao dete. (I missed the feeling of freedom I had as a child.)
8. Kada sam stigla, shvatila sam da mi *nije nedostajao* grad uopšte. (When I arrived, I realized that I didn't miss the city at all.)
9. *Nedostajalo* nam je vreme da završimo sve zadatke na vreme. (We were short on time to complete all the tasks on time.)
10. Ona je *nedostajala* svojoj porodici dok je bila na putovanju. (She missed her family while she was on a trip.)